HEADWORD: Nullifidian
<hw>Nul`li*fid"i*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>nullus</ets> none + <ets>fides</ets> faith.]</ety> <def>Of no
faith; also, not trusting to faith for salvation; -- opposed to
<ant>solifidian</ant>.</def> <rj><au>Feltham.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nullifidian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Nullifidian
<hw>Nul`li*fid"i*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An unbeliever.</def>
